<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="trust-vt">trust <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /trʌst/    美 /trʌst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>信任；相信：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>According to Anne, a true friend is a person whom you can trust. 
安妮认为，真正的朋友是一个你可以信任的人。</p><footer>人教① – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="i-trust-that">I trust (that)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[口语] 我希望…：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I trust that everything will go all right. 
我相信一切都会很顺利。</p></div></div>